  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nIn this issue https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/2197 we found that if a node advances on it's own to epoch 3 without having gossip enabled and then enables receiving blocks from other 3 nodes of the correct chain, it is not able to correctly sync and switch to the correct chain.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nAdd a sim test to purposely create that situation and ensure the node can recover\r\n\r\n",
